image, Portrait-style confrontation of Georg Carl von Döbeln and Russian commander Nikolaj Kamenskij, with the two armies forming distant background masses.

In the foreground, Döbeln and the Russian commander face one another — stern, composed, and inches apart — as columns of Swedish and Russian troops stretch away into the landscape behind them, lowered muskets and distant banners marking each force.
